    <title>Foresight Forums</title>

    <p>
        The Foresight Forums are a user community dedicated to Foresight, with users asking 
        help, tips and tricks about Foresight, and other related Foresight news and information. 
        The forums often link to content available on the Foresight Wiki.
        <link href="http://forum.foresightlinux.org/index.php">Click here to visit the Foresight 
        Forums</link>.
    </p>

    <p>
        To add or reply to threads on the Forums, you will need to create an account. This account 
        is separate from your JIRA and Wiki account. To create an account, click on <gui>register</gui> 
        just above the Search box in the upper right.
    </p>

